
Ranger Help for: survey(id)
===========================

SYNTAX:      survey/id
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   1
BASE SP:     2
SKILL TYPE:  knowledge

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to survey the type of terrain he or she is in.
You will note some characteristics of the area and make a decision as to
what terrain you are in. When a terrain is shown, it will be in its color.
Also, if your are in your range, primary or secondary terrains, they will
be show as well.

